The Alpha Pi class of Alpha Kappa Psi presents Disrupt & Decentralize: The Future of Blockchain. Our event is TOMORROW night at 7:00 PM at Chevron Auditorium, I-House. We will be featuring speakers from Coinbase, Ripple, IBM, Oracle, Ambisafe & Cisco! Learn more about the paradigm-shifting nature of blockchain technologies and interact with experts in the field. There will be FREE FOOD and beverages from CREAM, Chipotle, & Sliver. Network with recruiters and drop off a resume! RSVP to our event NOW using the link below and check out our Facebook Event to receive 5 extra tickets for our raffle prize, featuring a chance to win an iPhone X, Apple Airpods, and a Hydroflask!

https://goo.gl/forms/EpiGB5qmeWqXF9ZD3

https://www.facebook.com/events/417306328701715/
